Project PB 
==========

This is a mobile app using the Corona SDK and will be open-sourced during beta
for quality assurance. Licensing is TBD on what code is permissable for re-use.

INSTALLATION
============

Open using the Corona SDK Simulator. Open the file directory, select the
device to build for, and pick the main.lua file to start it up.

REQUIREMENTS
============

Version 2011.591 (2011.8.2) of the Corona Simulator on either Mac OS X 10.6+,
or windows 7+. 

WHAT'S NEXT
===========

Visit gamengineers.com/projectpb for more details, development roadmaps, 
support, and feedback. 

Robert Persaud
http://www.gamengineers.com
